commit 0e2214735901e60513d4119d496e715286b167b6
Author: Eric Kryski <ekryski@bidali.com>
Date:   Sun Mar 8 22:30:50 2026 -0600

    fix Parakeet V2 mel scale and add eval for joint output (#86)
    
    - Change mel filter scale from .slaney to .htk to match NeMo's
      AudioToMelSpectrogramPreprocessor defaults (both Parakeet V2 and V3
      were trained with NeMo using HTK mel scale)
    - Add eval(jointOut) calls in both TDT and standard RNN-T decode paths
      to ensure joint network output is materialized before argmax
    - Add parakeet-tdt-0.6b-v2 to supported models list
    
    Co-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

