commit e4910d5180aca24986e39f1d674fd42f1f8dfaa1
Author: Aleksandr Beshkenadze <beshkenadze@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Mar 9 00:51:29 2026 +0200

    feat: add MLXAudioLID module for spoken language identification (#80)
    
    * feat: add MLXAudioLID module for spoken language identification
    
    Add new MLXAudioLID SPM module implementing Wav2Vec2-based language
    identification (MMS-LID-256) supporting 256 languages.
    
    - Full Wav2Vec2 backbone: 7-layer feature extractor, feature projection,
      positional conv embedding, 48 transformer encoder layers
    - Custom attention matching HF key names (q_proj/k_proj/v_proj/out_proj)
    - Weight norm precomputed in sanitize() for positional conv embedding
    - Auto-normalization (zero-mean, unit-variance) in predict()
    - 18 tests: config, output types, sanitize (8 cases), model init/forward/predict, integration
    - LID smoke test with real facebook/mms-lid-256 model
    - README with quick start, API docs, and architecture overview
    
    * style: align LID module with codebase conventions
    
    - Replace Repo.ID force-unwrap with guard+throw LIDError.invalidRepoID
    - Remove redundant model.train(false) (eval(model) handles inference mode)
    - Read HF_TOKEN from env/Info.plist internally (match Qwen3ASR pattern)
    - Remove explicit config.json existence guard (let Data(contentsOf:) throw)
    - Qualify MLX.loadArrays for consistency with other modules
    - Upgrade verify: .noUnusedKeys to [.all] to catch missing weights
    - Add /// doc comments on all public methods
    
    * feat: add ECAPA-TDNN language identification model (VoxLingua107)
    
    Add second LID model supporting 107 languages via ECAPA-TDNN architecture
    from SpeechBrain. ~16x faster and ~47x smaller than MMS-LID-256.
    
    - EcapaTdnnConfig: Codable config with SpeechBrain-compatible defaults
    - EcapaMelSpectrogram: GPU-accelerated mel (Hamming, HTK, top_db=80)
    - EcapaTdnnLayers: TDNNBlock, Res2NetBlock, SEBlock, SERes2NetBlock, ASP
    - EcapaTdnnLID: full model with sanitize, fromPretrained, predict
    - 17 unit tests + 1 integration test (all passing)
    - README updated with both models documented
    
    * refactor: organize LID models into Models/ subdirectories
    
    Match the codebase convention used by TTS, STT, VAD, and Codecs modules:
    - Wav2Vec2 files → Models/Wav2Vec2/
    - EcapaTdnn files → Models/EcapaTdnn/
    - LIDOutput.swift and README.md remain at module root
    
    * fix: address CI failure and Copilot review feedback
    
    - Remove duplicate LIDSmokeTests struct from SmokeTests
    - Sort safetensors files before merging for deterministic loading
    - Wrap config.json loading in guard/exists check with LIDError.configNotFound
    - Add public init() to LanguagePrediction and LIDOutput
    - Cache Hamming window and mel filterbank as static properties
    - Remove unused MLXLMCommon dependency from MLXAudioLID target
    - Rename DNN property to dnn with @ModuleInfo(key:) annotation
    
    * fix: gate network tests behind MLXAUDIO_ENABLE_NETWORK_TESTS env var
    
    - Guard MMS-LID-256 and ECAPA-TDNN integration tests
    - Guard LID smoke test (downloads ~3.9GB model)
    - Replace fragile exact language assertion with confidence range check
    - Matches existing convention from VAD/STS test suites
    
    * refactor(codec): extract shared ECAPA-TDNN backbone
    
    * feat(tool): add lid cli demo
    
    * fix(lid): align ecapa inference with speechbrain
    
    * fix(lid): reuse shared DSP and drop GPL fixtures

